# Axero Page Builder – required docs

When working on Axero Page Builder, Raw HTML widgets, or Axero intranet code:

**Always consult:**
- `Docs/Tips for Coding in Page Builder.md` – coding tips, globals (CF_USERID, CF_SPACEID, etc.), CSS scoping, no `<head>`, button behavior, parser quirks (empty `{}`, JSON parser bugs for regex/backslashes, `aspnetForm` wrapper).
- `Docs/axero_documentation.json` – platform documentation, APIs, and feature reference.

When implementing or debugging **API calls** (REST, cases, content, widgets, etc.):
- Use `Docs/Axero Postman Collection.postman_collection.json` for endpoints, request shapes, and examples.

Paths are relative to the repo root. Prefer reading these files when answering questions or generating code for Axero.
